dc_description_s: This 1910 map shows Portland's quick east-side development and the beginning of south-east suburban sprawl.  This map comes from the "Greater Portland: Experiments with Professional Planning, 1905-1925", from the author's (Carl Abbott) own collection. Raster image georeferenced using WGS-84 pseudo mercator.
